# Cursor Config Repository Rules

## PowerShell Scripts
- Use ASCII markers ([OK], [ERROR], [WARN]) instead of emoji in Write-Host
- Check PowerShell reserved variables ($host, $input, $args) before use

## Docker & MCP Configuration
- Use Docker network (mcp-network) for inter-container communication
- Verify Docker image exists locally or on Docker Hub before use

## Script Lifecycle
- Prefer integrating fixes into existing scripts over temporary one-off scripts
